{"tid":1541123,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[缺一不可］英國會議會要求政府推動53個英聯邦國家給予香港人公民資格","createTime":"2019-09-04T13:38:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-05T15:23:49.000Z","uid":45983,"like":102,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"f512e4003813af5812af17425c8be4f559b8d578","tid":1541123,"uid":45983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:38:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190904&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=60010217\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190904%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D60010217&d=aWTYmjKPTw65bzRUwiqYJJtjV1Wc7Scp8ABb8MCffMw%3D&h=d91f4d56\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20190904%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D60010217&h=9c9bea06\" target=\"_blank\">https://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20190904&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=60010217</a><br />\n<br />\n香港「反送中」浪潮持續，即使特首林鄭月娥今天宣佈撤回修訂《逃犯條例》，但由於仍未回應民間另外四大訴求，民憤仍未平息。英國25位國會議員提出議案，呼籲英國不要「放棄」香港人之餘，更要求政府推動53個英聯邦國家給予香港人公民資格。"},{"pid":"aa7af1d09411fcf3f00e39fe6cb99885b1f6dd81","tid":1541123,"uid":212182,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:39:12.000Z","msg":"你地係咪仲天真以為呢個政府值得我地信任？仲信政府既承諾？點解唔向非法管治香港既中共說不？點解唔可以拎返主動權？點解仲甘願做中共奴隸？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/dOQLuS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/dOQLuS</a><br />\n要記住，香港唔係一個地方，係住呢度既人！我地先係香港既核心，香港既主人！無左我地，政府根本唔係一回事！點解要比依個草菅人命既政府拖住鼻子走！<br />\n有人以為宣告一國兩制同中英聯合聲明失效就會無西方國家幫手，其實唔啱<br />\n只要你將呢場運動變成自由民主vs極權主義<br />\n外國係無得唔幫。9月8日，不見不散！"},{"pid":"da72a89749be6ed2c0fdedd964490dce3273d5ac","tid":1541123,"uid":263448,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T13:39:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c11158a888364274b0cb620b814fdbcfd2850646","tid":1541123,"uid":92908,"lik